      "acceptanceCriteria": "Justification of the hemolysis power-law model form, turbulence closure, and non-Newtonian rheology assumptions must be provided with supporting literature evidence at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "The Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model was adopted without formal justification of its applicability to the VAD operating regime. Model form uncertainty is unquantified. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
    },
