    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors were reviewed against MRL 5 requirements. Seven factors were formally assessed; all seven achieved levels below required levels. Six factors were not assessed and represent unresolved epistemic gaps. Monte Carlo UQ was executed but covered only a subset of uncertain inputs. The overall credibility evidence package does not meet the minimum bar for MRL 5 acceptance. The assessment team formally records the decision as Not Accepted pending remediation of all identified gaps.",
